144
00:06:08,845 --> 00:06:10,108
Tell me honestly.

145
00:06:10,135 --> 00:06:11,135
Hmm?

146
00:06:12,545 --> 00:06:13,545
Why did you come back?

147
00:06:24,688 --> 00:06:26,281
To work, of course.

148
00:06:26,295 --> 00:06:27,368
That’s a weird question.

149
00:06:28,908 --> 00:06:30,905
There are so many other news stations.

150
00:06:34,355 --> 00:06:35,748
What do you really want?

151
00:06:40,895 --> 00:06:42,148
Who am I talking to?

152
00:06:43,525 --> 00:06:44,525
Huh?

153
00:06:46,415 --> 00:06:48,415
Why do you want to know about me?

154
00:06:50,785 --> 00:06:52,225
I thought we’d only talk about work.

155
00:06:52,685 --> 00:06:54,148
This is about work.

156
00:06:54,515 --> 00:06:57,101
You’re the reason my job is a mess.

157
00:06:57,135 --> 00:06:57,975
