183
00:10:36,355 --> 00:10:37,355
What’s up?

184
00:10:43,005 --> 00:10:44,241
I want to talk about work.

185
00:10:46,088 --> 00:10:47,088
Okay.

186
00:10:49,068 --> 00:10:51,065
If we can’t come to an agreement,

187
00:10:53,395 --> 00:10:54,915
