200
00:11:45,475 --> 00:11:46,521
Are you scared of me?

201
00:11:50,515 --> 00:11:53,095
You should keep up your image, Mr. Reporter.

202
00:11:57,985 --> 00:11:58,985
Deal.

203
00:12:00,105 --> 00:12:01,448
You and me…

204
00:12:02,735 --> 00:12:04,255
This should be fun, don’t you think?

205
00:12:08,705 --> 00:12:11,855
ST PERMSIN MARKET

206
00:12:12,975 --> 00:12:14,941
Okay. We’re just in time.

207
00:12:15,595 --> 00:12:17,075
We’re almost late, thanks to someone.

208
00:12:17,615 --> 00:12:18,948
Stop whining.

209
00:12:18,981 --> 00:12:20,315
My car’s in the shop.

210
00:12:20,755 --> 00:12:22,755
Besides, we were heading the same way anyway.

211
00:12:35,405 --> 00:12:37,548
