214
00:12:39,761 --> 00:12:40,881
It’s Yong’s.

215
00:12:40,901 --> 00:12:42,095
Where’s your car?

216
00:12:46,655 --> 00:12:47,701
It’s in the shop.

217
00:12:48,465 --> 00:12:49,581
