222
00:13:01,765 --> 00:13:02,765
Let’s go.

223
00:13:27,181 --> 00:13:28,168
Have you read the script?

224
00:13:28,201 --> 00:13:29,201
Yes.

225
00:13:29,475 --> 00:13:31,475
I think we should touch on capitalism too.

226
00:13:31,501 --> 00:13:33,421
