261
00:15:46,048 --> 00:15:46,588
Go!

262
00:15:46,615 --> 00:15:47,461
Shoo!

263
00:15:47,488 --> 00:15:49,268
Get out! You’re scaring my customers away!

264
00:15:49,295 --> 00:15:51,035
Why are you still here?

265
00:15:51,425 --> 00:15:52,501
Get out!

266
00:15:52,865 --> 00:15:54,475
